  337. module M = struct
  338.   (* Value expressions for the module language *)

  340.   let map sub {pmod_loc = loc; pmod_desc = desc; pmod_attributes = attrs} =
  341.     let open Mod in
  342.     let loc = sub.location sub loc in
  343.     let attrs = sub.attributes sub attrs in
  344.     match desc with
  345.     | Pmod_ident x -> ident ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub x)
  346.     | Pmod_structure str -> structure ~loc ~attrs (sub.structure sub str)
  347.     | Pmod_functor (param, body) ->
  348.         functor_ ~loc ~attrs
  349.           (map_functor_param sub param)
  350.           (sub.module_expr sub body)
  351.     | Pmod_apply (m1, m2) ->
  352.         apply ~loc ~attrs (sub.module_expr sub m1) (sub.module_expr sub m2)
  353.     | Pmod_apply_unit m1 ->
  354.         apply_unit ~loc ~attrs (sub.module_expr sub m1)
  355.     | Pmod_constraint (m, mty) ->
  356.         constraint_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.module_expr sub m)
  357.                     (sub.module_type sub mty)
  358.     | Pmod_unpack e -> unpack ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e)
  359.     | Pmod_extension x -> extension ~loc ~attrs (sub.extension sub x)

  361.   let map_structure_item sub {pstr_loc = loc; pstr_desc = desc} =
  362.     let open Str in
  363.     let loc = sub.location sub loc in
  364.     match desc with
  365.     | Pstr_eval (x, attrs) ->
  366.         let attrs = sub.attributes sub attrs in
  367.         eval ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub x)
  368.     | Pstr_value (r, vbs) -> value ~loc r (List.map (sub.value_binding sub) vbs)
  369.     | Pstr_primitive vd -> primitive ~loc (sub.value_description sub vd)
  370.     | Pstr_type (rf, l) -> type_ ~loc rf (List.map (sub.type_declaration sub) l)
  371.     | Pstr_typext te -> type_extension ~loc (sub.type_extension sub te)
  372.     | Pstr_exception ed -> exception_ ~loc (sub.type_exception sub ed)
  373.     | Pstr_module x -> module_ ~loc (sub.module_binding sub x)
  374.     | Pstr_recmodule l -> rec_module ~loc (List.map (sub.module_binding sub) l)
  375.     | Pstr_modtype x -> modtype ~loc (sub.module_type_declaration sub x)
  376.     | Pstr_open x -> open_ ~loc (sub.open_declaration sub x)
  377.     | Pstr_class l -> class_ ~loc (List.map (sub.class_declaration sub) l)
  378.     | Pstr_class_type l ->
  379.         class_type ~loc (List.map (sub.class_type_declaration sub) l)
  380.     | Pstr_include x -> include_ ~loc (sub.include_declaration sub x)
  381.     | Pstr_extension (x, attrs) ->
  382.         let attrs = sub.attributes sub attrs in
  383.         extension ~loc ~attrs (sub.extension sub x)
  384.     | Pstr_attribute x -> attribute ~loc (sub.attribute sub x)
  385. end

  387. module E = struct
  388.   (* Value expressions for the core language *)

  390.   let map sub {pexp_loc = loc; pexp_desc = desc; pexp_attributes = attrs} =
  391.     let open Exp in
  392.     let loc = sub.location sub loc in
  393.     let attrs = sub.attributes sub attrs in
  394.     match desc with
  395.     | Pexp_ident x -> ident ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub x)
  396.     | Pexp_constant x -> constant ~loc ~attrs (sub.constant sub x)
  397.     | Pexp_let (r, vbs, e) ->
  398.         let_ ~loc ~attrs r (List.map (sub.value_binding sub) vbs)
  399.           (sub.expr sub e)
  400.     | Pexp_fun (lab, def, p, e) ->
  401.         fun_ ~loc ~attrs lab (map_opt (sub.expr sub) def) (sub.pat sub p)
  402.           (sub.expr sub e)
  403.     | Pexp_function pel -> function_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.cases sub pel)
  404.     | Pexp_apply (e, l) ->
  405.         apply ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (List.map (map_snd (sub.expr sub)) l)
  406.     | Pexp_match (e, pel) ->
  407.         match_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (sub.cases sub pel)
  408.     | Pexp_try (e, pel) -> try_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (sub.cases sub pel)
  409.     | Pexp_tuple el -> tuple ~loc ~attrs (List.map (sub.expr sub) el)
  410.     | Pexp_construct (lid, arg) ->
  411.         construct ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub lid) (map_opt (sub.expr sub) arg)
  412.     | Pexp_variant (lab, eo) ->
  413.         variant ~loc ~attrs lab (map_opt (sub.expr sub) eo)
  414.     | Pexp_record (l, eo) ->
  415.         record ~loc ~attrs (List.map (map_tuple (map_loc sub) (sub.expr sub)) l)
  416.           (map_opt (sub.expr sub) eo)
  417.     | Pexp_field (e, lid) ->
  418.         field ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (map_loc sub lid)
  419.     | Pexp_setfield (e1, lid, e2) ->
  420.         setfield ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e1) (map_loc sub lid)
  421.           (sub.expr sub e2)
  422.     | Pexp_array el -> array ~loc ~attrs (List.map (sub.expr sub) el)
  423.     | Pexp_ifthenelse (e1, e2, e3) ->
  424.         ifthenelse ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e1) (sub.expr sub e2)
  425.           (map_opt (sub.expr sub) e3)
  426.     | Pexp_sequence (e1, e2) ->
  427.         sequence ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e1) (sub.expr sub e2)
  428.     | Pexp_while (e1, e2) ->
  429.         while_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e1) (sub.expr sub e2)
  430.     | Pexp_for (p, e1, e2, d, e3) ->
  431.         for_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.pat sub p) (sub.expr sub e1) (sub.expr sub e2) d
  432.           (sub.expr sub e3)
  433.     | Pexp_coerce (e, t1, t2) ->
  434.         coerce ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (map_opt (sub.typ sub) t1)
  435.           (sub.typ sub t2)
  436.     | Pexp_constraint (e, t) ->
  437.         constraint_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (sub.typ sub t)
  438.     | Pexp_send (e, s) ->
  439.         send ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (map_loc sub s)
  440.     | Pexp_new lid -> new_ ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub lid)
  441.     | Pexp_setinstvar (s, e) ->
  442.         setinstvar ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s) (sub.expr sub e)
  443.     | Pexp_override sel ->
  444.         override ~loc ~attrs
  445.           (List.map (map_tuple (map_loc sub) (sub.expr sub)) sel)
  446.     | Pexp_letmodule (s, me, e) ->
  447.         letmodule ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s) (sub.module_expr sub me)
  448.           (sub.expr sub e)
  449.     | Pexp_letexception (cd, e) ->
  450.         letexception ~loc ~attrs
  451.           (sub.extension_constructor sub cd)
  452.           (sub.expr sub e)
  453.     | Pexp_assert e -> assert_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e)
  454.     | Pexp_lazy e -> lazy_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e)
  455.     | Pexp_poly (e, t) ->
  456.         poly ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e) (map_opt (sub.typ sub) t)
  457.     | Pexp_object cls -> object_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.class_structure sub cls)
  458.     | Pexp_newtype (s, e) ->
  459.         newtype ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s) (sub.expr sub e)
  460.     | Pexp_pack me -> pack ~loc ~attrs (sub.module_expr sub me)
  461.     | Pexp_open (o, e) ->
  462.         open_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.open_declaration sub o) (sub.expr sub e)
  463.     | Pexp_letop {let_; ands; body} ->
  464.         letop ~loc ~attrs (sub.binding_op sub let_)
  465.           (List.map (sub.binding_op sub) ands) (sub.expr sub body)
  466.     | Pexp_extension x -> extension ~loc ~attrs (sub.extension sub x)
  467.     | Pexp_unreachable -> unreachable ~loc ~attrs ()

  469.   let map_binding_op sub {pbop_op; pbop_pat; pbop_exp; pbop_loc} =
  470.     let open Exp in
  471.     let op = map_loc sub pbop_op in
  472.     let pat = sub.pat sub pbop_pat in
  473.     let exp = sub.expr sub pbop_exp in
  474.     let loc = sub.location sub pbop_loc in
  475.     binding_op op pat exp loc

  477. end

  479. module P = struct
  480.   (* Patterns *)

  482.   let map sub {ppat_desc = desc; ppat_loc = loc; ppat_attributes = attrs} =
  483.     let open Pat in
  484.     let loc = sub.location sub loc in
  485.     let attrs = sub.attributes sub attrs in
  486.     match desc with
  487.     | Ppat_any -> any ~loc ~attrs ()
  488.     | Ppat_var s -> var ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s)
  489.     | Ppat_alias (p, s) -> alias ~loc ~attrs (sub.pat sub p) (map_loc sub s)
  490.     | Ppat_constant c -> constant ~loc ~attrs (sub.constant sub c)
  491.     | Ppat_interval (c1, c2) ->
  492.         interval ~loc ~attrs (sub.constant sub c1) (sub.constant sub c2)
  493.     | Ppat_tuple pl -> tuple ~loc ~attrs (List.map (sub.pat sub) pl)
  494.     | Ppat_construct (l, p) ->
  495.         construct ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub l)
  496.           (map_opt
  497.              (fun (vl, p) -> List.map (map_loc sub) vl, sub.pat sub p)
  498.              p)
  499.     | Ppat_variant (l, p) -> variant ~loc ~attrs l (map_opt (sub.pat sub) p)
  500.     | Ppat_record (lpl, cf) ->
  501.         record ~loc ~attrs
  502.                (List.map (map_tuple (map_loc sub) (sub.pat sub)) lpl) cf
  503.     | Ppat_array pl -> array ~loc ~attrs (List.map (sub.pat sub) pl)
  504.     | Ppat_or (p1, p2) -> or_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.pat sub p1) (sub.pat sub p2)
  505.     | Ppat_constraint (p, t) ->
  506.         constraint_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.pat sub p) (sub.typ sub t)
  507.     | Ppat_type s -> type_ ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s)
  508.     | Ppat_lazy p -> lazy_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.pat sub p)
  509.     | Ppat_unpack s -> unpack ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s)
  510.     | Ppat_open (lid,p) -> open_ ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub lid) (sub.pat sub p)
  511.     | Ppat_exception p -> exception_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.pat sub p)
  512.     | Ppat_extension x -> extension ~loc ~attrs (sub.extension sub x)
  513. end

  515. module CE = struct
  516.   (* Value expressions for the class language *)

  518.   let map sub {pcl_loc = loc; pcl_desc = desc; pcl_attributes = attrs} =
  519.     let open Cl in
  520.     let loc = sub.location sub loc in
  521.     let attrs = sub.attributes sub attrs in
  522.     match desc with
  523.     | Pcl_constr (lid, tys) ->
  524.         constr ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub lid) (List.map (sub.typ sub) tys)
  525.     | Pcl_structure s ->
  526.         structure ~loc ~attrs (sub.class_structure sub s)
  527.     | Pcl_fun (lab, e, p, ce) ->
  528.         fun_ ~loc ~attrs lab
  529.           (map_opt (sub.expr sub) e)
  530.           (sub.pat sub p)
  531.           (sub.class_expr sub ce)
  532.     | Pcl_apply (ce, l) ->
  533.         apply ~loc ~attrs (sub.class_expr sub ce)
  534.           (List.map (map_snd (sub.expr sub)) l)
  535.     | Pcl_let (r, vbs, ce) ->
  536.         let_ ~loc ~attrs r (List.map (sub.value_binding sub) vbs)
  537.           (sub.class_expr sub ce)
  538.     | Pcl_constraint (ce, ct) ->
  539.         constraint_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.class_expr sub ce) (sub.class_type sub ct)
  540.     | Pcl_extension x -> extension ~loc ~attrs (sub.extension sub x)
  541.     | Pcl_open (o, ce) ->
  542.         open_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.open_description sub o) (sub.class_expr sub ce)

  544.   let map_kind sub = function
  545.     | Cfk_concrete (o, e) -> Cfk_concrete (o, sub.expr sub e)
  546.     | Cfk_virtual t -> Cfk_virtual (sub.typ sub t)

  548.   let map_field sub {pcf_desc = desc; pcf_loc = loc; pcf_attributes = attrs} =
  549.     let open Cf in
  550.     let loc = sub.location sub loc in
  551.     let attrs = sub.attributes sub attrs in
  552.     match desc with
  553.     | Pcf_inherit (o, ce, s) ->
  554.         inherit_ ~loc ~attrs o (sub.class_expr sub ce)
  555.           (map_opt (map_loc sub) s)
  556.     | Pcf_val (s, m, k) -> val_ ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s) m (map_kind sub k)
  557.     | Pcf_method (s, p, k) ->
  558.         method_ ~loc ~attrs (map_loc sub s) p (map_kind sub k)
  559.     | Pcf_constraint (t1, t2) ->
  560.         constraint_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.typ sub t1) (sub.typ sub t2)
  561.     | Pcf_initializer e -> initializer_ ~loc ~attrs (sub.expr sub e)
  562.     | Pcf_attribute x -> attribute ~loc (sub.attribute sub x)
  563.     | Pcf_extension x -> extension ~loc ~attrs (sub.extension sub x)

  565.   let map_structure sub {pcstr_self; pcstr_fields} =
  566.     {
  567.       pcstr_self = sub.pat sub pcstr_self;
  568.       pcstr_fields = List.map (sub.class_field sub) pcstr_fields;
  569.     }

  571.   let class_infos sub f {pci_virt; pci_params = pl; pci_name; pci_expr;
  572.                          pci_loc; pci_attributes} =
  573.     let loc = sub.location sub pci_loc in
  574.     let attrs = sub.attributes sub pci_attributes in
  575.     Ci.mk ~loc ~attrs
  576.      ~virt:pci_virt
  577.      ~params:(List.map (map_fst (sub.typ sub)) pl)
  578.       (map_loc sub pci_name)
  579.       (f pci_expr)
  580. end

  582. (* Now, a generic AST mapper, to be extended to cover all kinds and
  583.    cases of the OCaml grammar.  The default behavior of the mapper is
  584.    the identity. *)

  586. let default_mapper =
  587.   {
  588.     constant = C.map;
  589.     structure = (fun this l -> List.map (this.structure_item this) l);
  590.     structure_item = M.map_structure_item;
  591.     module_expr = M.map;
  592.     signature = (fun this l -> List.map (this.signature_item this) l);
  593.     signature_item = MT.map_signature_item;
  594.     module_type = MT.map;
  595.     with_constraint = MT.map_with_constraint;
  596.     class_declaration =
  597.       (fun this -> CE.class_infos this (this.class_expr this));
  598.     class_expr = CE.map;
  599.     class_field = CE.map_field;
  600.     class_structure = CE.map_structure;
  601.     class_type = CT.map;
  602.     class_type_field = CT.map_field;
  603.     class_signature = CT.map_signature;
  604.     class_type_declaration =
  605.       (fun this -> CE.class_infos this (this.class_type this));
  606.     class_description =
  607.       (fun this -> CE.class_infos this (this.class_type this));
  608.     type_declaration = T.map_type_declaration;
  609.     type_kind = T.map_type_kind;
  610.     typ = T.map;
  611.     type_extension = T.map_type_extension;
  612.     type_exception = T.map_type_exception;
  613.     extension_constructor = T.map_extension_constructor;
  614.     value_description =
  615.       (fun this {pval_name; pval_type; pval_prim; pval_loc;
  616.                  pval_attributes} ->
  617.         Val.mk
  618.           (map_loc this pval_name)
  619.           (this.typ this pval_type)
  620.           ~attrs:(this.attributes this pval_attributes)
  621.           ~loc:(this.location this pval_loc)
  622.           ~prim:pval_prim
  623.       );

  625.     pat = P.map;
  626.     expr = E.map;
  627.     binding_op = E.map_binding_op;

  629.     module_declaration =
  630.       (fun this {pmd_name; pmd_type; pmd_attributes; pmd_loc} ->
  631.          Md.mk
  632.            (map_loc this pmd_name)
  633.            (this.module_type this pmd_type)
  634.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pmd_attributes)
  635.            ~loc:(this.location this pmd_loc)
  636.       );

  638.     module_substitution =
  639.       (fun this {pms_name; pms_manifest; pms_attributes; pms_loc} ->
  640.          Ms.mk
  641.            (map_loc this pms_name)
  642.            (map_loc this pms_manifest)
  643.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pms_attributes)
  644.            ~loc:(this.location this pms_loc)
  645.       );

  647.     module_type_declaration =
  648.       (fun this {pmtd_name; pmtd_type; pmtd_attributes; pmtd_loc} ->
  649.          Mtd.mk
  650.            (map_loc this pmtd_name)
  651.            ?typ:(map_opt (this.module_type this) pmtd_type)
  652.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pmtd_attributes)
  653.            ~loc:(this.location this pmtd_loc)
  654.       );

  656.     module_binding =
  657.       (fun this {pmb_name; pmb_expr; pmb_attributes; pmb_loc} ->
  658.          Mb.mk (map_loc this pmb_name) (this.module_expr this pmb_expr)
  659.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pmb_attributes)
  660.            ~loc:(this.location this pmb_loc)
  661.       );


  664.     open_declaration =
  665.       (fun this {popen_expr; popen_override; popen_attributes; popen_loc} ->
  666.          Opn.mk (this.module_expr this popen_expr)
  667.            ~override:popen_override
  668.            ~loc:(this.location this popen_loc)
  669.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this popen_attributes)
  670.       );

  672.     open_description =
  673.       (fun this {popen_expr; popen_override; popen_attributes; popen_loc} ->
  674.          Opn.mk (map_loc this popen_expr)
  675.            ~override:popen_override
  676.            ~loc:(this.location this popen_loc)
  677.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this popen_attributes)
  678.       );

  680.     include_description =
  681.       (fun this {pincl_mod; pincl_attributes; pincl_loc} ->
  682.          Incl.mk (this.module_type this pincl_mod)
  683.            ~loc:(this.location this pincl_loc)
  684.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pincl_attributes)
  685.       );

  687.     include_declaration =
  688.       (fun this {pincl_mod; pincl_attributes; pincl_loc} ->
  689.          Incl.mk (this.module_expr this pincl_mod)
  690.            ~loc:(this.location this pincl_loc)
  691.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pincl_attributes)
  692.       );


  695.     value_binding =
  696.       (fun this {pvb_pat; pvb_expr; pvb_constraint; pvb_attributes; pvb_loc} ->
  697.          let map_ct (ct:Parsetree.value_constraint) = match ct with
  698.            | Pvc_constraint {locally_abstract_univars=vars; typ} ->
  699.                Pvc_constraint
  700.                  { locally_abstract_univars = List.map (map_loc this) vars;
  701.                    typ = this.typ this typ
  702.                  }
  703.            | Pvc_coercion { ground; coercion } ->
  704.                Pvc_coercion {
  705.                  ground = Option.map (this.typ this) ground;
  706.                  coercion = this.typ this coercion
  707.                }
  708.          in
  709.          Vb.mk
  710.            (this.pat this pvb_pat)
  711.            (this.expr this pvb_expr)
  712.            ?value_constraint:(Option.map map_ct pvb_constraint)
  713.            ~loc:(this.location this pvb_loc)
  714.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pvb_attributes)
  715.       );


  718.     constructor_declaration =
  719.       (fun this {pcd_name; pcd_vars; pcd_args;
  720.                  pcd_res; pcd_loc; pcd_attributes} ->
  721.         Type.constructor
  722.           (map_loc this pcd_name)
  723.           ~vars:(List.map (map_loc this) pcd_vars)
  724.           ~args:(T.map_constructor_arguments this pcd_args)
  725.           ?res:(map_opt (this.typ this) pcd_res)
  726.           ~loc:(this.location this pcd_loc)
  727.           ~attrs:(this.attributes this pcd_attributes)
  728.       );

  730.     label_declaration =
  731.       (fun this {pld_name; pld_type; pld_loc; pld_mutable; pld_attributes} ->
  732.          Type.field
  733.            (map_loc this pld_name)
  734.            (this.typ this pld_type)
  735.            ~mut:pld_mutable
  736.            ~loc:(this.location this pld_loc)
  737.            ~attrs:(this.attributes this pld_attributes)
  738.       );

  740.     cases = (fun this l -> List.map (this.case this) l);
  741.     case =
  742.       (fun this {pc_lhs; pc_guard; pc_rhs} ->
  743.          {
  744.            pc_lhs = this.pat this pc_lhs;
  745.            pc_guard = map_opt (this.expr this) pc_guard;
  746.            pc_rhs = this.expr this pc_rhs;
  747.          }
  748.       );



  752.     location = (fun _this l -> l);

  754.     extension = (fun this (s, e) -> (map_loc this s, this.payload this e));
  755.     attribute = (fun this a ->
  756.       {
  757.         attr_name = map_loc this a.attr_name;
  758.         attr_payload = this.payload this a.attr_payload;
  759.         attr_loc = this.location this a.attr_loc
  760.       }
  761.     );
  762.     attributes = (fun this l -> List.map (this.attribute this) l);
  763.     payload =
  764.       (fun this -> function
  765.          | PStr x -> PStr (this.structure this x)
  766.          | PSig x -> PSig (this.signature this x)
  767.          | PTyp x -> PTyp (this.typ this x)
  768.          | PPat (x, g) -> PPat (this.pat this x, map_opt (this.expr this) g)
  769.       );
  770.   }

  1081. let run_main mapper =

  1084.     let n = Array.length a in
  1085.     if n > 2 then

  1092.       in

  1094.     else begin
  1095.       Printf.eprintf "Usage: %s [extra_args] <infile> <outfile>\n%!"
  1096.                      Sys.executable_name;

  1098.     end
  1099.   with exn ->

  1101.     exit 2
